    <text>
        <body>
            <pb facs="" xml:id="leaf001r" type="recto"/>
            <div1 type="poem">
               
                <head type="main-authorial">THE BAD EXAMPLE</head>
            
            
                <lg type="stanza">
                
                    <l>They made me choose between <interp type="marxist-rhetoric">selling out</interp><ptr target="#no1">1</ptr> and the wall</l>
                    <l> and it was a wall of knives. </l>
                    </lg>
                    <lg>
                    <l>And since I couldn't help getting cut up</l>
                    <l>son of the worst plague they said to me </l>
                    <l><interp type="marxist-rhetoric">he doesn't love his blood</interp><ptr target="#no2">2</ptr> </l>
                    <l>refuses to keep it in </l>
                    <l>and unties the knots of his veins. </l>
                    <l></l>
                    <l></l>
                    <l></l>
                    <l></l>
                </lg>
                <lg>
                <l>Outraged all the mothers in the city wouldn't weep </l>
                <l>that day not even for the slit throats of the onions. </l>
                </lg>
                <lg>
                 <l> I hope at least the little children will come unto me. </l>
                 </lg>
              <note type="editorial" target="#hsm"> [HSM] </note>
            </div1>
            <note xml:id="no1"></note>
            <note xml:id="no2"></note>
        </body>
